<section class="wp-block-argc-intro-1 container text-center" id="Section0"><div class="container top-bottom-space"><div class="row"><div class="col-sm-12  wow fadeInUp"><h1 class="main-title">Welcome to Creek Marina Yacht Club</h1><div class="max-width"><p class="small-text mtp10">Discover Creek Marina Yacht Club, The Heart of the Creek. A prestigious marina set in an iconic waterfront development on the banks of the historic Dubai Creek. Our secure and sheltered berthing houses over 80 yachts offering our members a luxury berthing location with the stunning skyline views of Dubai.</p></div></div></div></div></section>



<section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-right content-section overlapping-section container nonoverlap ranches-restaurant"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3 order-last order-sm-first"><div class="content-box box-top-minus text-left text-sm-left"><div class="icon-image-block"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Marina.svg"><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Marina.svg"></noscript></div><h4 class="">Berthing Enquiry Form</h4><div class="small-text desc">For more information about our berthing packages, click on the button below and fill out the form. One of our Team will then be in touch with all the details.</div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="https://form.typeform.com/to/qhMRDZYb" title="ENQUIRY FORM">ENQUIRY FORM</a></div></div><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 order-first order-sm-last wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block img-right-minus center" data-lazy-src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Marina-Page-CMYC-LRL.jpg.webp"/><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Marina-Page-CMYC-LRL.jpg.webp" class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block img-right-minus center"/></noscript></div></div></div></div></section>



<section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-left content-section overlapping-section overlap img-at-top"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 wow fadeInLeft" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="img-fluid img-left-minus mx-auto d-block" data-lazy-src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Main-Page-Berthing-LRL-1.jpg.webp"/><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Main-Page-Berthing-LRL-1.jpg.webp" class="img-fluid img-left-minus mx-auto d-block"/></noscript></div></div><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3"><div class="content-box  text-left text-sm-left"><div class="icon-image-block"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Berthing.svg"><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Berthing.svg"></noscript></div><h4 class="">Berthing</h4><div class="small-text desc">As a member you can benefit from 24/7 assistance for departure and arrival from our dock hand and security teams.</div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="/berthing/" title="SEE MORE">SEE MORE</a></div></div></div></div></section>



<section class="wp-block-argc-overlap-section-right content-section overlapping-section overlap img-at-top mbp60"><div class="container"><div class="row align-items-center"><div class="col-sm-5 col-xl-3 order-last order-sm-first"><div class="content-box box-top-minus text-left text-sm-left"><div class="icon-image-block"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" data-lazy-src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rally-Programme.svg"><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Rally-Programme.svg"></noscript></div><h4 class="">Rally Programme</h4><div class="small-text desc">A fun and memorable yachting experience visiting coastline locations around the UAE with like-minded boaters.</div><a class="btn btn-outline-info border-btn" href="/rallies/" title="SEE MORE">SEE MORE</a></div></div><div class="col-sm-7 col-xl-9 order-first order-sm-last wow fadeInRight" data-wow-duration="1.25s"><div class="lg-img-box"><img decoding="async" src="data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20viewBox='0%200%200%200'%3E%3C/svg%3E" class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block img-right-minus center" data-lazy-src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Main-Page-Rally-LRL-copy.jpg.webp"/><noscript><img decoding="async" src="https://www-creekmarinayachtclub-com.azureedge.net/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Main-Page-Rally-LRL-copy.jpg.webp" class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block img-right-minus center"/></noscript></div></div></div></div></section>



